Class KtQuat

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Quaternion
camzup.kotlin.KtQuat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Quaternion>
public class KtQuat extends Quaternion
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for quaternions.
